Package: mccoursepack
Type: Package
Title: Course Materials and Weekly Scaffolds for MC 451 and MC 501
Version: 01.08.01
Authors@R: person("AP", "Leith", email = "apleith@siue.edu", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Provides student-facing scaffolds (Quarto templates and starter files)
 for weekly work in MC 451 and MC 501. Students install or update the package
 and use helper functions to copy the appropriate week's materials into a
 local working directory.
